.SH PLATFORM NOTES
.TP
.B Target OS
CentOS\|/\|RHEL 7.7, 7.8, 7.9.
Package manager:
.BR yum (1)
(never dnf).
Container runtime: Docker CE (docker\-ce RPM).
.TP
.B Kubernetes
Version \(<=\|1.21.  Installed via kubernetes.io RPM repository
(kubelet, kubeadm, kubectl).
.TP
.B OpenShift
OKD\|/\|OCP 3.11.  API groups:
.IR apps.openshift.io/v1 ,
.IR route.openshift.io/v1 ,
.IR image.openshift.io/v1 ,
.IR security.openshift.io/v1 .
.TP
.B Collibra edge
DGC Edge node.  Requires
.I java\-11\-openjdk .
Default ports: HTTP 7080, HTTPS 7443.
firewalld zone XML generated by
.BR generate_collibra_edge_config .
.TP
.B SELinux
Enforcing mode assumed on all target nodes.  Generated pod specs include
.IR seLinuxOptions.type\|=\|spc_t .
.TP
.B Claude model
.I claude\-opus\-4\-6
with
.IR thinking={\(dqtype\(dq:\(dqadaptive\(dq} .
Streaming enabled; adaptive thinking dynamically controls reasoning depth.
.
